type: Superalgos Review - Amazing Tool Lots of Potential

definition.text:
New to the investing world, though I've followed cryptocurrency since the birth of BitCoin. Came across this wonderful program and had the best tutorial experience I've ever come across. It's clear that this project will be going places in the future. I look forward to learning it!

--breguard
